OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's school says pupils
OL,4,C'less stressed' after mobile phone ban
OL,6,FBrianna Ghey's school has banned
OL,7,Fmobile phones during the day in a move
OL,8,Fwhich has "reduced" pupils' stress
OL,9,Flevels, the headteacher said.
OL,11,FEmma Mills, head of Birchwood
OL,12,FCommunity High School in Warrington,
OL,13,FCheshire, told The Mirror that special
OL,14,Fpouches used to lock students' phones
OL,15,Fduring the day were introduced in
OL,16,FSeptember.
