OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's school says pupils
OL,4,C'less stressed' after mobile phone ban
OL,6,FHer comments come amid calls from the
OL,7,FNational Education Union (NEU) and
OL,8,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch for
OL,9,Fthe Government to bring in a statutory
OL,10,Fban on mobile phones in schools.
OL,12,FMs Mills said the move is "allowing
OL,13,Fkids to be kids again", with pupils
OL,14,Fnot able to open the pouches until
OL,15,Fhome time.
