OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's school says pupils
OL,4,C'less stressed' after mobile phone ban
OL,6,FShe told the newspaper: "Around
OL,7,Fschool, there is more chatter in the
OL,8,Fcorridors at breaks and lunch,
OL,9,Fstudents are more focused in lessons
OL,10,Fand the number attending House
OL,11,Fcompetitions and enrichment activities
OL,12,Fhas risen."
OL,14,FShe added: "Students say they like the
OL,15,F'break' from it. They say it has
OL,16,Freduced their stress levels knowing
OL,17,Fthey don't have to think about what is
OL,18,Fhappening.
