OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's school says pupils
OL,4,C'less stressed' after mobile phone ban
OL,6,F"It has made them realise they can
OL,7,Flive without it. With 23 years in
OL,8,Feducation, I have seen, over time, the
OL,9,Fimpact that phones and social media
OL,10,Fhave had on young people.
OL,12,F"Seeing how our behaviour and
OL,13,Fsafeguarding issues around phones and
OL,14,Fthe online world have nearly
OL,15,Fdisappeared feels like a big moment."
OL,17,FBrianna's mother Esther Ghey supports
OL,18,Fa "blanket ban" on smartphones in
OL,19,Fschools across the country, previously
OL,20,Fciting concerns over how these devices
OL,21,Fcan be misused by students.
