OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's school says pupils
OL,4,C'less stressed' after mobile phone ban
OL,6,FShe told The Mirror: "I'm incredibly
OL,7,Fproud of the steps Birchwood High
OL,8,FSchool has taken.
OL,10,F"Brianna often struggled with
OL,11,Fdistraction in school due to her
OL,12,Fsmartphone and social media use, and I
OL,13,Ftruly believe this initiative would
OL,14,Fhave made a meaningful difference for
OL,15,Fher."
