OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's school says pupils
OL,4,C'less stressed' after mobile phone ban
OL,6,FScarlett Jenkinson and Eddie
OL,7,FRatcliffe, both 15 at the time, lured
OL,8,FBrianna to Culcheth Linear Park in
OL,9,FWarrington where the 16-year-old was
OL,10,Ffatally stabbed 28 times with a
OL,11,Fhunting knife in February 2023.
OL,13,FJenkinson was sentenced at Manchester
OL,14,FCrown Court in December 2023 to a
OL,15,Fminimum sentence of 22 years in
OL,16,Fprison, and Ratcliffe to a minimum
OL,17,Fterm of 20 years.
OL,19,FThe court heard that Jenkinson became
OL,20,F"obsessed" with Brianna after joining
OL,21,FBirchwood High in October 2022.
