OL,6,FThe teenagers were discussing
OL,7,FBrianna's murder for weeks, detailed
OL,8,Fin Jenkinson's handwritten murder plan
OL,9,Fand phone messages found by detectives.
OL,11,FJenkinson, while aged 14, downloaded a
OL,12,FTOR internet browser app, to watch
OL,13,Fvideos of the torture and murder of
OL,14,Freal people, in "red rooms" on the
OL,15,F"dark web".
