OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's school says pupils
OL,4,C'less stressed' after mobile phone ban
OL,6,FShe grew an interest in serial
OL,7,Fkillers, making notes on their methods
OL,8,Fand admitted enjoying "dark fantasies"
OL,9,Fabout killing and torture, with the
OL,10,Fpair living in a secret world of
OL,11,Fwarped interests in murder and
OL,12,Fcruelty, the trial heard.
OL,14,FSchools in England were given non-
OL,15,Fstatutory guidance under the former
OL,16,FConservative government in February
OL,17,Flast year intended to stop the use of
OL,18,Fphones during the school day.
